4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge, aiming to become cybersecurity specialists in just 16 weeks. The program includes foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced topics like cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. There are 3 live online classes per week with a maximum class size of 16. Participants will receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions upon finishing. The course can be taken in English or Spanish, and no previous experience is needed. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop